\c 21
\s Jeremiya anoporofita kuti Jerusarema richaparadzwa
\p
\v 1 Shoko, rakasvika kuna Jeremiya kubva kuna Jehovha mambo Zedhekiya paakatuma kwaari Pashuri mwanakomana waMarikija, naZefaniya mwanakomana waMaaseya mupristi, achiti:
\v 2 Tibvunzire hako kuna Jehovha, nokuti Nebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi anoita hondo nesu, zvimwe Jehovha angatiitira zvinoenderana nemabasa ake anoshamisa, kuti akwire kubve kwatiri.
\p
\v 3 Zvino Jeremiya wakati kwavari: Muchareva seizvi kuna Zedhekia:
\v 4 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri: Tarira, ndichadzosa zvombo zvehondo zviri mumaoko ako, zvaunorwisa nazvo mambo weBhabhironi neVaKaradhiya vanokukombai kunze kwemasvingo, uye ndichavaunganidza pakati peguta rino:
\v 5 Zvino ini ndomene ndichakurwisa neruoko rwakatandavadzwa, uye neruoko rwune simba, uye mukutsamwa nemukupfuta uye nehasha huru.
\v 6 Zvino ndicharova vagari vemuguta rino, munhu pamwe nechipfuwo, vachafa nekuda kwedenda guru.
\v 7 Zvino pashure, anoreva Jehovha, ndichapa Zedhekia mambo waJudha, nevaranda vake, nevanhu, vakasara muguta rino, padenda, nepamunondo, nepanzara, muruoko rwaNebhukadhineari mambo weBhabhironi, nemuruoko rwvavengi vavo, nemuruoko rweavo vanotsvaka upenyu hwavo, uye achavarova nekwakapinza kwemunondo, uye haangavaregi kana kuvanzwira tsitsi, kana kuvanzwira ngoni.
\p
\v 8 Zvino uchati kuvana ava: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Tarira, ndakaisa pamberi pako nzira yeupenyuIwe uti kuvanhu ava: Zvanzi naJehovha: Tarirai, ndinoisa pamberi penyu nzira yohupenyu nenzira yorufu.
\v 9 Ani nani unorambira muguta rino uchaurawa nomunondo nenzara nehosha; asi ani nani unobuda akaenda kuVaKaradhiya vanokukombai, iye uchararama, hupenyu hwake huchava kwaari chinhu chaakapamba.
\v 10 Nokuti zvanzi naJehovha: Ndakarinzira guta rino chiso changu kuti ndiriitire zvakaipa, ndirege kuriitira zvakanaka; richaiswa mumaoko amambo weBhabhironi, iye ucharipisa nomoto.
\p
\v 11 Zvino kana iri imba yamambo waJudha, inzwai shoko raJehovha:
\v 12 Nhai imba yaDhavhidhi ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha tongai zvakarurama mangwanani, murwire wakabirwa muruoko rwounomumanikidza, kuti kutsamwa kwangu kurege kubuda somoto, kuchipfuta kusina ungakudzima, nokuda kwezvakaipa zvamabasa enyu.
\v 13 Tarira, ndine mhosva newe, iwe ugere mumupata, padombo romubani ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha; imi, munoti: Ndiani uchapinda mudzimba dzedu?
\v 14 Ndichakurovai zvakaenzana nezvibereko zvamabasa enyu ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha; ndichabatidza moto mudondo raro, uchapedza zvese zvakaripoteredza.
